The Student Data Manager is basically a digital system that helps schools, colleges, and universities manage their institution-related information in a structured and organized way.
Instead of keeping details on paper or random files, this program stores everything in a proper format, making it super easy to add, search, update, and save institutional data.

The app supports three types of institutions:
School
College
University
Each entry stores details like:
Institution name
Location
Ratings
Number of streams/courses
Availability of hostel, mess, and labs
Number of students

The idea is to make a simple management tool that works like a mini-database system for academic institutions.
